## 5. super()ã®æ­£ã—ã„ä½¿ã„æ–¹

### ğŸ“– super()ã¨ã¯

è¦ªã‚¯ãƒ©ã‚¹ã®ãƒ¡ã‚½ãƒƒãƒ‰ã‚’å‘¼ã³å‡ºã™ãŸã‚ã®é–¢æ•°ã€‚

### ğŸ¯ super()ã®3ã¤ã®ç”¨é€”

#### ç”¨é€”1: ã‚³ãƒ³ã‚¹ãƒˆãƒ©ã‚¯ã‚¿ã§è¦ªã‚’åˆæœŸåŒ–

```python
class Parent:
    def __init__(self, name):
        self.name = name

class Child(Parent):
    def __init__(self, name, age):
        super().__init__(name)  # è¦ªã‚’åˆæœŸåŒ–
        self.age = age
```

#### ç”¨é€”2: ã‚ªãƒ¼ãƒãƒ¼ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ‰ã—ãŸãƒ¡ã‚½ãƒƒãƒ‰ã§è¦ªã‚’å‘¼ã¶

```python
class Parent:
    def greet(self):
        print("ã“ã‚“ã«ã¡ã¯")

class Child(Parent):
    def greet(self):
        super().greet()  # è¦ªã®greetã‚’å‘¼ã¶
        print("ç§ã¯å­ã§ã™")
```

#### ç”¨é€”3: å¤šé‡ç¶™æ‰¿ã§MROã«å¾“ã£ã¦å‘¼ã¶

```python
class A:
    def method(self):
        print("A")

class B(A):
    def method(self):
        print("B")
        super().method()  # MROã«å¾“ã£ã¦Aã‚’å‘¼ã¶

class C(A):
    def method(self):
        print("C")
        super().method()

class D(B, C):
    def method(self):
        print("D")
        super().method()  # MRO: D â†’ B â†’ C â†’ A

d = D()
d.method()
# å‡ºåŠ›:
# D
# B
# C
# A
```

### âš ï¸ super()ã®æ³¨æ„ç‚¹

#### æ³¨æ„1: super().__init__()ã‚’å¿˜ã‚Œã‚‹

```python
class Parent:
    def __init__(self, name):
        self.name = name

class Child(Parent):
    def __init__(self, age):
        # super().__init__()ã‚’å¿˜ã‚Œã¦ã„ã‚‹
        self.age = age

child = Child(10)
print(child.





